reviewText: Did not get my 2 year old boy's attention right now but maybe later.

This DVD contains ten episodes from The Adventures Of Chuck & Friends cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. The Checkup
2. Chucks Perfect Plans
3. Trucks Vs. Wild
4. Kid Stuff
5. As The Engine Coughs
6. Beach Blanket Uh-Oh
7. Fender Bender
8. Sleep-Driving Chuck
9. Mind Your Own Business
10. The Pothole
